name: verifyClosedAccountsForExternalFirm()

children.description: Q3 - Retrieve data from DB2: closed EJ accounts
Q1 - Retrieve data from DB2: relationships for Branch with closed and non-closed EJ accounts

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select rlt.RLTSHP_ID AS RELID,
sum(case when sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is null then 1 else 0 end) as closed_count,
sum(case when sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is null then 0 else 1 end) as non_closed_count

from PROD.RLTSHP_13120 rlt
join PROD.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_DTL_13088 grp on rlt.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID = grp.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID
join PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc on sub_acc.ACCT_ID=grp.ACCT_ID

where 
rlt.ISO_CTRY_CD = 'US'
and sub_acc.BR_NO = 9979

group by rlt.RLTSHP_ID
having sum(case when sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is null then 1 else 0 end) > 0 and 
sum(case when sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is null then 0 else 1 end) > 0
